PrecisAuthority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the Province of NEWFOUNDLAND which provides for the implementation, on a cost-shared basis, of educational, housing and community development programs, as well as water and sewer projects, in the Inuit communities of Labrador (Hopedale, Makkovik, Nain, Postville and Rigolet).

precis:
Authority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the Province of
NEWFOUNDLAND which provides for the implementation, on a cost-shared basis,
of educational, housing and community development programs, as well as
water and sewer projects, in the Inuit communities of Labrador (Hopedale,
Makkovik, Nain, Postville and Rigolet).
